Graph, DP

Use DP to solve this problem. Let dp[i][j][k] be the arbitrage of maximum profits from country i to country j with k intermediate countries. So the result will be among dp[i][i][k] for some i and k.
To print the path of arbitrage, use another array prev[i][j][k] to trace the previous country.

0.010s in uva 104
0.000s in poj 1238

